Just washed my hair and this is your sign to stop skipping your heat protection step 😌✨

Here’s how I style my hair post-wash without compromising on health or hold with @bbluntindia 💁‍♀️👇

🔥 Step 1: I spray on the BBLUNT Hot Shot Heat Protection Mist to shield my strands from heat damage.
Infused with grapeseed oil and provitamin B5, it not only protects but also leaves my hair soft, shiny & oh-so-touchable 💧🍇

💨 Step 2: Once styled, I lock it in with the BBLUNT Hot Shot Hold Spray for that firm yet flexible hold - no crunch, no residue, just natural-looking definition that lasts all day 💫

These two are a total dream team for effortless, salon-like styling at home. Easy, breezy, and heat-safe, my hair is loving the attention 💕
